1.NVDLA硬件组成：Convolution Core，Single Data Processor ，Planar Data Processor，Channel Data Processor ，Dedicated Memory and Data Reshape Engines 
2.Small system:  headless NVDLA
   Large system: headed NVDLA
3.two modes of operation: independent mode, fused mode
4.Connections: CSB interface, Interrupt interface, DBB interface
